<p class="govuk-body-l govuk-!-margin-top-6">
  You've just experienced <a href="https://localgovims.digital" class="govuk-link">LocalGov IMS</a> — an open-source income management system designed for UK councils. In 20 minutes, you've seen the full income cycle: citizen payments, transaction management, suspense resolution, daily reconciliation, and bank file processing.
</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">What you've learned</h2>

<div class="ndx-takeaway-grid">
  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">&#x1f4b3;</span>
      GOV.UK Pay integration
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      LocalGov IMS integrates directly with GOV.UK Pay, the government's shared payment platform. Citizens pay securely through a familiar, accessible interface. Payments flow automatically into the income management system with full audit trails.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Reduced payment processing costs, PCI DSS compliance handled by GOV.UK Pay
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">&#x1f50d;</span>
      Efficient suspense management
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Unallocated payments are flagged immediately and presented in a clear workflow. Finance officers can search, match, and allocate payments quickly, keeping suspense balances low and audit-ready.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Reduced suspense balances, faster resolution, audit compliance
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">&#x1f4ca;</span>
      Daily reconciliation
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      eReturns provide a daily snapshot of all income received, broken down by payment method and fund. This is the foundation of accurate financial reporting and ensures that no income is lost or misallocated.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Accurate financial reporting, daily controls, reduced audit risk
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">&#x1f3e6;</span>
      Bank reconciliation
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Automated bank file import and matching means that reconciliation — traditionally one of the most labour-intensive finance tasks — can be completed in minutes rather than hours.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Hours saved per week on reconciliation, fewer manual errors
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Production readiness</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  This demo runs the same codebase that can be used in production. For a full deployment, you'd additionally want:
</p>

